                        <interp inst="t18680608-506-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The prisoner was subsequently <rs id="t18680608-506-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
